# Email Configuration for Contact Form
# Follow the setup guide in EMAIL_SETUP_GUIDE.md

# Your Gmail address (the account that will SEND the emails)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com

# Your Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password)
# Generate at: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
EMAIL_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx

# Three admin emails that will receive form submissions
# These are the people who will be notified when someone submits the contact form
EMAIL_RECIPIENT_1=kandledirectpublishing@gmail.com
EMAIL_RECIPIENT_2=second-admin-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_RECIPIENT_3=third-admin-email@gmail.com

# Note: You can use the same email multiple times if you don't have 3 different emails
# Example:
# EMAIL_RECIPIENT_1=admin@example.com
# EMAIL_RECIPIENT_2=admin@example.com
# EMAIL_RECIPIENT_3=support@example.com
